    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-06-25T08:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-06-25T08:00:00-05:00" n="838"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d838">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">124.613/1142: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-06-25T16:00:00+03:00"
                            >June 25, 1941—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 5 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1216. Notwithstanding the most extreme pressure on the Foreign Office since the
                    outbreak of hostilities, and despite repeated assurances that transportation for
                    11 members of the Embassy staff and baggage would be provided on the train
                    leaving for Vladivostok last night, no transportation was provided although the
                    train left on schedule with a few foreigners but mostly Soviet citizens. The
                    Foreign Office has renewed its assurances that transportation will be provided
                    tonight.</p>
                <p>I trust that the Department will make it clear to Oumanski that it expects the
                    Soviet authorities to extend to the Embassy every facility possible during the
                    present critical period.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
